&lt;p&gt;Would you like to be part of something special and work with a dedicated nurse specialist team?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen to recruit an inspirational, energetic and enthusiastic nurse specialist to join the Colposcopy Service. The successful candidate will be part of a skilled team of consultants and nurse specialists that aim to support the Trust and the Gynaecology Service in delivering the standards set out by the BSCCP. As an individual, you will act as expert in this specialist area of Colposcopy and have experience in the wider Gynaecology Service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Trust is looking to recruit a trained Nurse Colposcopist with BSCCP accreditation. In addition, there is an expectation that the successful candidate would provide some support to the Clinical Nurse Specialist for Gynaecological Cancers as per service requirements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic and knowledgeable candidate who can support the development of the service, deliver the highest standard of patient care, and demonstrate our Trust Values: ‘Safe, personal, respectful, responsibility’.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be expected to motivate others and be an excellent role model. You will work closely with the lead clinician to improve operational efficiency and enhance the performance of the colposcopy service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The working hours for this role are 37.5 per week. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are interested in this post, you are encouraged to contact either of our Clinical Nurse Specialist for an informal discussion / visit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NamePolly JedrzejakJob titleClinical Nurse Specuialist Colposcopy / Nurse ColposcopistEmail addresspolly.jedrzejak@nhs.netTelephone number020 8510 5164Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Polly Jedrzejak, polly.jedrzejak@nhs.net, or telephone: 020 8510 5555 extension 4709.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you wish to visit the Women’s Health Centre , please contact Polly Jedrzejak by email.&lt;/p&gt;
